ign-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-5-768x613.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe facade comprises precision-cast concrete panels, serving a dual purpose: it delivers a distinctive aesthetic and moderates the desert climate. The perforated outer shell takes cues from traditional Middle Eastern shading techniques, reinterpreting them through a contemporary lens. The result is a surface that not only reduces heat gain but also mirrors the intricate patterns etched into desert landscapes by shifting sands and winds.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573033\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573033\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-6-810x554.jpg\" alt=\"Interior of a modern architectural space with geometric patterns on walls and ceiling. People in traditional attire walk through the area.\" width=\"810\" height=\"554\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-6-810x554.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-6-800x547.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-6-768x525.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573034\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573034\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Stat