h-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-9-810x569.jpg\" alt=\"Futuristic train station interior with large, curved ceiling and patterned walls. People walk along the platform, some in traditional attire, reflecting on the polished floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-9-810x569.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-9-800x562.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-9-768x539.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInternally, the station is arranged across four levels and includes six platforms, creating a seamless multi-modal experience for commuters. ZHA’s meticulous design process prioritized functionality as much as form – balancing spatial elegance with structural efficiency. Elements such as passive cooling strategies, energy-efficient systems, and responsive climate controls contribute to a significantly reduced carbon footprint.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573037\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573037\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-10-810x1139.jpg\" alt=\"People ascend an escalator inside a modern building with a futuristic design featuring geometric skylights and curved surfaces.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1139\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-10-810x1139.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-10-800x1125.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-