etro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-14-810x665.jpg\" alt=\"People walking in modern, futuristic train station with curved architectural design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"665\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-14-810x665.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-14-800x657.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-14-768x631.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn the first 11 weeks alone, over 18 million passengers used the station, which is now a symbol of Riyadh’s ambition to harmonize cutting-edge architecture with sustainable urban growth. The KAFD Metro Station exemplifies how thoughtful design can elevate everyday experiences, transforming routine travel into an encounter with visionary urbanism.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573042\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573042\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-15-810x696.jpg\" alt=\"People walking and standing at a modern, spacious subway station with geometric ceiling design and sliding glass doors.\" width=\"810\" height=\"696\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-15-810x696.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-15-800x688.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-15-768x660.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/KAFD-Metro-Station-Riyadh-Saudi-Arabia-Zaha-Hadid-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto,